403
00:22:57,400 --> 00:22:58,400
It’s you again, Pun?

404
00:22:58,680 --> 00:23:00,000
I sing well, right?

405
00:23:00,840 --> 00:23:02,080
It’s good you’re here.

406
00:23:02,120 --> 00:23:04,120
Please put Pun away.

407
00:23:04,480 --> 00:23:06,200
Toey, come over here.

408
00:23:10,920 --> 00:23:13,120
I’ll sit there.

409
00:23:13,160 --> 00:23:14,600
