413
00:23:18,000 --> 00:23:18,800
Someone is watching over you.

414
00:23:18,840 --> 00:23:19,960
I’m so envious.

415
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:21,280
Your boyfriend is watching over you.

416
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:22,400
- Alright, then.
- 	No.

417
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:23,720
No.

418
00:23:23,760 --> 00:23:24,800
Come with me.

419
00:23:24,840 --> 00:23:26,240
Let Q sing properly.

420
00:23:26,280 --> 00:23:27,680
I can sing well, too.

421
00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:30,840
Listen to Q sing.

422
00:23:31,200 --> 00:23:32,600
Show me how you sing.

423
00:23:32,640 --> 00:23:33,320
