00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:27,160
Nothing.

448
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:27,920
Nothing?

449
00:24:43,440 --> 00:24:46,120
♪ As long as we have each other ♪

450
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:48,320
♪ Spending every day together ♪

451
00:24:48,360 --> 00:24:50,880
♪ As long as we stand next to each other ♪

452
00:24:50,920 --> 00:24:52,880
♪ That’s all that matters ♪

453
00:24:52,920 --> 00:24:59,760
♪ Unshaken, come what may ♪

454
00:24:59,800 --> 00:25:03,720
♪ With your hand in mine, we’re okay ♪

