00:25:03,760 --> 00:25:05,960
♪ Together, we are ♪

456
00:25:06,840 --> 00:25:08,040
Do you want to go anywhere after this?

457
00:25:10,880 --> 00:25:12,000
I can’t think of any.

458
00:25:13,000 --> 00:25:14,400
Let’s go home then.

459
00:25:15,960 --> 00:25:18,160
Let’s go to Oh’s cafe.

460
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:21,320
Since Q has already left,

461
00:25:21,360 --> 00:25:24,160
