469
00:25:31,120 --> 00:25:31,800
Don’t leave yet.

470
00:25:31,840 --> 00:25:32,880
Eh? Beer?

471
00:25:32,920 --> 00:25:33,560
Beer.

472
00:25:33,600 --> 00:25:34,640
Don’t leave me.

473
00:25:34,680 --> 00:25:35,680
