478
00:25:47,200 --> 00:25:47,720
Huh?

479
00:25:47,840 --> 00:25:48,600
Nothing.

480
00:25:51,320 --> 00:25:52,040
Ready?

481
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:59,200
Sitting with you here again reminds me of the day

