500
00:27:09,440 --> 00:27:11,120
(Q, you’re handsome today.)

501
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:12,520
(You looked so cool while playing music.)

502
00:27:30,320 --> 00:27:31,880
(What did Peem gossip about me?)

503
00:27:50,600 --> 00:27:53,440
(He called you a playboy, who kept changing the girls you dated.)

504
00:28:06,640 --> 00:28:07,760
(I’ll deal with him.)

505
00:28:08,120 --> 00:28:09,960
Hey, don’t.

506
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:12,080
That’s not all he said.

507
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:13,600
