509
00:28:17,240 --> 00:28:20,000
because….

510
00:28:20,160 --> 00:28:21,800
Because?

511
00:28:22,480 --> 00:28:26,360
Because you’re only serious about one person now.

512
00:28:26,520 --> 00:28:27,760
Do you believe him?

513
00:28:28,040 --> 00:28:29,400
