525
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:01,200
Really?

526
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:03,640
I guess the connection wasn’t good.

527
00:31:05,720 --> 00:31:06,440
I don’t know,

528
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:09,960
but I think this doesn’t seem right.

529
00:31:13,200 --> 00:31:14,560
So, throughout this time,

530
00:31:15,840 --> 00:31:17,160
what have I done wrong?

531
00:31:19,680 --> 00:31:22,480
Fang, how’s your brother doing now?

532
00:31:22,520 --> 00:31:24,080
He called me yesterday.

533
00:31:24,120 --> 00:31:26,480
He said things are going well there.

534
00:31:26,800 --> 00:31:28,880
He’ll make time to come back here at the end of this year.

535
00:31:30,240 --> 00:31:31,760
Next Tuesday,

536
00:31:31,800 --> 00:31:35,320
